# Stranded Trains

## Overview

A web app for tracking stranded trains, designed for railway control rooms

## Feature

- Track stranded train status and duration
- Carry out stranded passenger risk assessment
- Alert over due communication with the stranded train
- Export individual stranded train data to PDF
- Export all data via API

## Tech Stack

- Node.js backend
- JS Frontend
- SQLite Database

## Getting Started

- npm install
- npm run build
- npm run start
